elements.name: TS_RegisteredCheckout_01 - Registered User of 6thstreet.com site should be able to place order using store credit if it is enabled

steps.name: User enters valid login details "validuser" username and "validuser" password in the login popup
user enters product name as "LCW-8S7179Z4-LCW-TURQUOIS" in search text box and click search icon
user clicks on product tile in result
user selects countrySize as "EU", size as "10Y"
user navigates to shopping bag page and clicks on proceedToCheckout button
user enters the valid details for shipping address
